This project has a {{frontendFramework}} frontend. Validate frontend-specific contracts and component paths.
{{/if}}
{{#if hasBackend}}
This project has a{{#if backendFramework}} {{backendFramework}}{{/if}} backend. Validate API contracts, DTOs, and service paths.
{{/if}}
